com.vtls.opensource.oai
Class Harvester

java.lang.Object
  com.vtls.opensource.oai.Harvester

public class Harvester
extends Object

This object will connect to an oai provider and harvest its records. It can harvest an entire repository, records between certain dates, and/or records in certain sets.

Author:
Chris Hall
